aboutContainer.title: WHO WE ARE
aboutContainer.description: With Bootstrap 2, we added optional mobile friendly styles for key aspects of the framework. With Bootstrap 3, weve rewritten the project to be mobile friendly from the start. Instead of adding on optional mobile styles, theyre baked right into the core. In fact, Bootstrap is mobile first. Mobile first styles can be found throughout the entire library instead of in separate files.
